- Prefer LTS or widely adopted stable versions
- Avoid versions with known CVEs unless no alternative
- Ensure compatibility with:
  - Spring Boot BOMs
  - Common enterprise stacks
- Detect and preserve:
  - Parent POM inheritance
  - DependencyManagement overrides

